name: SimpleMix
description:
SIMPLE MIX

Simple Is Better

Now, You can run SimpleMix ON Tensor.Art

go get some coffe, and start typing....

btw, you can buy Me coffe too

SociaBuzz ❤️

Prompt Sugestion:

Positive

best quality, masterpiece, photorealistic, high resolution, 8K raw photo, 1girl,

Negative:

ng_deepnegative_v1_75t, bad-hands-5, watermark, signature, username, text, nude, nipple, nipples, worst quality, low quality, normal quality, (missing hands, missing legs, missing finger), (extra hands, extra legs, extra finger), (bad hands, bad legs, bad finger), BadNegAnatomyV1-neg, badhandv4, simple background, greyscale, monochrome, cropped, jpeg artifacts, blurry, ugly, duplicate, mutilated, mutated, mutation, deformed, poorly drawn hands, poorly drawn face, malformed limbs, extra limbs, cloned face, disfigured, bad proportions

Recommended Parameters:

Sampler: DPM++ 2M Karras, DPM++ SDE Karras

Steps: 20~40

Hires upscaler: 4x-UltraSharp, R-Ersgan 4x

Hires upscale: 2

Hires steps: 10~15

Denoising strength: 0.3~0.5

CFG scale: 6-8,5

clip skip 1 or 2

deppend on your settings..!!!!

Thats it...
